Usage info

The following notes describe what the ChatNVIDIA integration supports. The ChatNVIDIA integration supports `invoke`, `stream`, and their async variants. It also supports tool use. Because ChatNVIDIA is meant for use with many types of models, it doesn’t have function calling support.

